all of his repeated traumas.

723
00:41:46,712 --> 00:41:48,923
I think that influenced
his character-building greatly.

724
00:41:49,006 --> 00:41:51,467
What if, in order to break away
from the negativity,

725
00:41:52,718 --> 00:41:56,138
